      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Lead Scoring & CRM Sync\n\n**Flow:**\n1. Webhook receives lead data\n2. Seeds test data fallbacks\n3. Validates email\n4. Scores 0–90 (budget + source + co. size)\n5. Creates HubSpot contact\n6. Logs to internal CRM\n7. Notifies Slack in batches\n\n**Tiers:**\n🔴 Hot  70+  → Senior team\n🟡 Warm 40–69 → Standard\n⚪ Cold  <40  → Nurture",
